Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧,武一郎!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多坏达大人对你所干的事非常愤怒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎样负起这个责任?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多支达路将军竟有怪罪他人的资格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己的错你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你多余的插手才令翔龙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,虎王成为了渡的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗最重要是讲求纪委的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个人的任意行为我武一郎是不会饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四十话\N恐怖的愤怒力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人面岩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,那个很像火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超美人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我发现好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人对着笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊?虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要背!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,放我下来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊?虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你精神点了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么悲伤的面孔不衬你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,我想也想不到会再见到虎王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到我高兴吗?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和渡果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好-朋-友!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来玩兵捉贼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来场很没干的赛跑决胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不跟你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然火美子是第一名呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是终点了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我加入吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我弄倒不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我使出东哥罗传受的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀,惩罚特别版吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!混蛋们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的生气了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!喂,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…请…请停手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道你是救世主渡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还做出了那种事,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这拿迪加村是绝对不能愤怒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那样对待还要我不生气?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要生气…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长先生,为什么不可以生气的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个布斯卡布像便是原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本那个是叫猫猫伦像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是传播快乐的神像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个像看见愤怒的话便会发生大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条村便会被炸得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此便阻止我们生气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为支配这第六星界的黑暗魔术士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控占领了神圣的大地亚索加的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的黑暗火炎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的仇敌渡的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我死亡遥控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他们在拿迪加村吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里应是有布斯加布像在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界山第一占卜师图星婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有没有人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在找星界山第一占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图星婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的占卜从没错过的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,难道你便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是星界山第一大占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图星婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆?可是,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我这样却已有三千岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个大婆婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"是吗?"是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你正在寻找的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会因巨大的邪恶力量而苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的邪恶力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力量不但是救世主渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:10:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连魔界之王多坏达也可比美的绝大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多…多坏达?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙现在在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你,图星小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大地之父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请我的力量赐予你生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我的魔力变成的魔少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,到渡他们那里!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是,死亡遥控大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子那家伙去哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,老虎仔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然找不到火子,但这女孩在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈重要的遗物手镯被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个红色头发的男孩抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手持着鱼叉很粗鲁的又可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不就是海火子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我收声!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是那个叫死亡遥控的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法造出来的土公仔啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是他把我重要的手镯抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要被骗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个了,那是我妈妈的遗物!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,你掉了东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是这女孩的手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要还给她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?那我还给她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蠢材…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蠢材啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,不可以生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布斯加布像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不可以生气?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以不生气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要啊海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很糟了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来搔你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收声!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…你们会明白我的心情吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是什么人在干扰我的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷龙剑在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有绝大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在占卜我们的秘密吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们这样做的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星界的波士死亡遥控啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好好看清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说得没错了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不对,海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,我不信你说的话是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不相信同伴是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向海火子道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫做道歉?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得真是对不起别人时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子低下头,希望对方原谅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样低下头,说对不起啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我也要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪得…看不过眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟可看穿我的魔少女是假的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了呢,龙星丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,死与死!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它是用泥土造的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以自由变形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超飞龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死与死是我用魔力造的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个程度的攻击是打不倒它的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再变形了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样打也打不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎样做才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那水晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水晶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那家伙打散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞄准里面的水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要失手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形,飞龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身,老虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼豪拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛虎剑攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙光击拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有和多坏达比美的力量的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这件事我怎样也想不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会在神圣的亚索加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打败死亡遥控的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们比赛谁在到达亚索加前道歉得最多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是服了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

